  QuestId: Trial of Culling 2
  QuestTitle: Trial of Culling 2
  QuestObjective: Kill 15 Minions
  QuestDescription: You are commanded to carry the 'Package' to a lonely cabin deep
    within the whispering woods. The task is to be done far from prying eyes, where
    only the spirits of the forest may judge your actions. What is done with the
    Package once you arrive is your burden to decide, and silence is required until
    the deed is complete.
  QuestOutcome: You sense no gratitude will follow your task, only silence... and
    the faint impression that something unseen is taking careful note of how efficiently
    you end a life.
  MaxProgress: 15
